"不惜丧心病狂。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4936cd0455"},{"id":"3ecbf4d60e","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4936cd0455"},{"id":"377bc29c2d","type":"paragraph","text":"生平不喜逢迎，","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4936cd0455"},{"id":"9cee3bbc24","type":"paragraph","text":"至始最恨诌媚，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4936cd0455"},{"id":"51958bfc7e","type":"paragraph","text":"纵然有才又有德，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4936cd0455"},{"id":"dd1001f481","type":"paragraph","text":"总不被人尝识，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4936cd0455"},{"id":"dba9560b01","type":"paragraph","text":"提薪提级无望，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4936cd0455"},{"id":"bf99984d62","type":"paragraph","text":"落后分子有你，","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4936cd0455"},{"id":"d13977071e","type":"paragraph","text":"几年还是起码级，","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4936cd0455"},{"id":"a7e43f55ac","type":"paragraph","text":"怎不叫人掩（咽）气。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4936cd0455"}],"page":{"id":"ee5a906469","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4936cd0455","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}